## API Response Format
The OpenWeatherMap API returns JSON data like:
```json
{
  "name": "London",
  "sys": {"country": "GB"},
  "main": {
    "temp": 15,
    "feels_like": 14,
    "temp_min": 12,
    "temp_max": 18,
    "humidity": 72,
    "pressure": 1013
  },
  "weather": [{"description": "partly cloudy"}],
  "wind": {"speed": 4.5},
  "clouds": {"all": 45},
  "sys": {"sunrise": 1234567890, "sunset": 1234567890}
}
```

